{"tid":620203,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母 TB真係好撚核突","createTime":"2018-04-07T11:10:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T13:02:40.000Z","uid":164634,"like":22,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a0f4cf2f339ea8b3975ade77dc0821e4bbac0567","tid":620203,"uid":164634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T11:10:06.000Z","msg":"頭先睇新聞<br />\n最後果part介紹黑警做單手掌上壓幫殘疾動物酬款<br />\n破左Guinness record<br />\n<br />\n本來都好地地<br />\n一訪問個男警<br />\n黑黑實實 細眼 梳個油頭<br />\n正路香港男性look<br />\n<br />\n但佢一開口<br />\n嘩 屌你老母<br />\n女人聲黎既<br />\n睇睇個名 孔逸娜<br />\n咁女性化既名<br />\n有男人既外型<br />\n又一聲女人聲<br />\n<br />\n我個心即刻what the fuck is this?<br />\n可能因為我眼見同聽既野有咁大<br />\n仲有啲嘔心既感覺 (認真冇誇大)<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔敢相信自己睇緊咩<br />\n先唔講電視上哩隻生物鐘意男定女<br />\n但正常人都唔會扮到opposite sex <br />\n認真為咩<br />\n我睇完之係有種好核突既感覺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/190952_42da5527d7450ffa93c188196a4b808d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F190952_42da5527d7450ffa93c188196a4b808d.png&h=61ed190b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/191004_ad48f47bc48257d11b18be98b37bb853.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F191004_ad48f47bc48257d11b18be98b37bb853.png&h=91a08176&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"220240cdf0cecea25e3650b127e1245dd9b90071","tid":620203,"uid":116530,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T11:10:58.000Z","msg":"成個男人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a3127fc613e1b09ec57e20089c0534479afd60b","tid":620203,"uid":156149,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T11:11:42.000Z","msg":"佢用男廁定女廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0096749b74734a80be84d5a740ccfbaae287d89f","tid":620203,"uid":25601,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedB